  "body": "Now that nodes can run Windows or Linux, we can no longer assume Tiller will be scheduled to a Linux node. \r\n\r\nOn such clusters, `helm init` often fails when the Tiller pod is scheduled to a Windows node. Perhaps we could hardcode a node selector with `beta.kubernetes.io/os=linux` as an easy workaround?",
